        <h2 class="s-title">Best Activities</h2>
        <div class="item-list">
          <div class="item">
            <div class="item-body">
              <div class="item-name">Perimeter Ride — M-185</div>
              <div class="item-desc">8 miles flat, car-free, full shoreline. The only state highway with no motor vehicles. 1.5–2 hrs.</div>
