            </div>
            <div class="item-badge ib-free">Free</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="item-body">
              <div class="item-name">Sugar Loaf + Skull Cave</div>
              <div class="item-desc">75-ft limestone pillar and a cave from the 1763 Pontiac War. Unsigned interior trails. Nobody goes here.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="item-badge ib-free">Free</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="item-body">
              <div class="item-name">Fort Mackinac</div>
