          <div class="srow">
            <div class="stime">Afternoon</div>
            <div class="stext">Drive the <strong>M-119 Tunnel of Trees</strong> toward Cross Village — 20 miles of old-growth canopy arching over Lake Michigan bluffs. Go both directions.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="srow">
            <div class="stime">Evening</div>
            <div class="stext">Dinner at <strong>Legs Inn</strong> (Cross Village) — Polish roadhouse on a Lake Michigan bluff, ~$16/person. Best meal of the trip.</div>
          </div>
